references: Related: Res 7592, Res 7601, Res 7602. Repealing: Ord 68547
summary: An ordinance providing for the improvement of East 65th Street, from 35th Avenue Northeast to 50th Avenue Northeast, and from Princeton Avenue to Sand Point Way, and other streets and avenues, by Resurfacing, Paving, etc.; accepting the offer of King County as set forth in Resolution Nos. 7592 and 7602 of the Board of County Commissioners; appropriating money therefor; and repealing Ordinance No. 68547.
